description: Bay Area's First Burmese Food Truck.Sharing borders with India, China, Laos and Thailand, Burmese cuisine is influenced by the spices, seasonings, ingredients, and cooking styles of its neighbors. We bring the freshest ingredients & most flavorful spices to create authentic Burmese dishes. Specialties include Tea Leaf Salad, Indian Curry Oxtail & Moh Hinga (Catfish Noodle Soup).
name: Lil Burma
